<lb n="0293a08" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0293001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】明本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此經與麗本大異故別載之</note><title>佛說穰麌梨童女經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0293a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0293a10" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0293002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔唐〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0293002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唐【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0293002"><lem wit="【大】">唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三藏沙門大廣智不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0293a11" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT21p0293a1101">如是我聞。一時薄伽梵。住舍衛國祇樹給
<lb n="0293a12" ed="T"/>孤獨園。與大苾芻眾千二百五十人俱。復
<lb n="0293a13" ed="T"/>有無量菩薩摩訶薩。及諸天龍藥叉乾闥
<lb n="0293a14" ed="T"/>婆阿修羅迦樓羅緊那羅摩睺羅伽人非人
<lb n="0293a15" ed="T"/>等皆來集會。爾時世尊告諸苾芻。我念往
<lb n="0293a16" ed="T"/>昔。住雪山北遊香醉山。見一童女。百福相
<lb n="0293a17" ed="T"/>好莊嚴其身。鹿皮為衣以諸毒蛇而為瓔
<lb n="0293a18" ed="T"/>珞。將諸毒<note n="0293003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蟲＝蠱【宋】＊</note><note n="0293003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟲【大】＊，蠱【宋】＊</note><app n="0293003"><lem wit="【大】">蟲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">蠱</rdg></app><note n="0293004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蚖蝮＝蟒蛇ィ【甲】</note><note n="0293004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蚖蝮【大】，蟒蛇【校異-甲】</note><app n="0293004"><lem wit="【大】">蚖蝮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">蟒蛇</rdg></app>之類。前後圍繞常為
<lb n="0293a19" ed="T"/>伴戲。飲<note n="0293005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（諸）＋毒ィ【甲】</note><note n="0293005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毒【大】，諸毒【校異-甲】</note><app n="0293005"><lem wit="【大】">毒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">諸毒</rdg></app><note n="0293006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">漿＋（及）ィ【甲】</note><note n="0293006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漿【大】，漿及【校異-甲】</note><app n="0293006"><lem wit="【大】">漿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">漿及</rdg></app>食毒果。彼女見我謂言。仁
<lb n="0293a20" ed="T"/>者當知聽我宣說穰麌<note n="0293007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梨＋（童女）ィ【甲】</note><note n="0293007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梨【大】，梨童女【校異-甲】</note><app n="0293007"><lem wit="【大】">梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">梨童女</rdg></app>真<note n="0293008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＋（法）ィ【甲】</note><note n="0293008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，言法【校異-甲】</note><app n="0293008"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">言法</rdg></app>。能除世
<lb n="0293a21" ed="T"/>間一切諸毒。若人聞此真言。及持我名者。
<lb n="0293a22" ed="T"/>不被一切諸毒<note n="0293009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所＝傷ィ【甲】</note><note n="0293009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所【大】，傷【校異-甲】</note><app n="0293009"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">傷</rdg></app>害。爾時童女為我宣說。
<lb n="0293a23" ed="T"/>我從彼女聞已。常持此法饒益有情。我今
<lb n="0293a24" ed="T"/>當說真言曰。</p>
